# {{context|transitive|lang=en}} To irritate by rubbing; [[chafe]]. {{defdate|First attested in the mid 18<sup>th</sup> century.}}<ref name=SOED/>
# {{context|transitive|lang=en}} To cause the surface to become more rough.
# {{context|intransitive|lang=en}} To undergo [[abrasion]].

